text: The Datt Kyaik Hill bent-toed gecko (Cyrtodactylus dattkyaikensis) is a species of gecko endemic to Myanmar. ==References== * http://reptile- database.reptarium.cz/species?genus=Cyrtodactylus&species;=dattkyaikensis Category:Reptiles of Myanmar Category:Cyrtodactylus Category:Reptiles described in 2020 Category:Taxa named by Larry Lee Grismer Category:Taxa named by Perry L.
